70.
Pre-order (Root-Left-Right):
Visit the root node.
Traverse the left subtree.
Traverse the right subtree.

In-order (Left-Root-Right):
Traverse the left subtree.
Visit the root node.
Traverse the right subtree.

Post-order (Left-Right-Root):
Traverse the left subtree.
Traverse the right subtree.
Visit the root node.

